feat: implement P5, P9, P15, P16, P17, P18 from AI-MODULE-ACTION-PLAN

P5 (SSE Streaming) — already implemented; verified sendMessageStreaming, streaming
  state, animate-pulse cursor, AbortController ref and i18n keys in AiAssistantPage.tsx.

P9 (RAG semantic with pgvector-compat) — add EmbeddingJson to AIKnowledgeSource entity
  and EF config; IEmbeddingCacheService + NullEmbeddingCacheService + InMemoryEmbeddingCacheService;
  ScopedEmbeddingProviderProxy (avoids captive dependency); EmbeddingIndexJob background job
  (30-min PeriodicTimer, indexes sources with null EmbeddingJson via IEmbeddingProvider);
  DocumentRetrievalService cosine-similarity scoring with backward-compatible 3-arg ctor;
  migration 20260413214000_AddEmbeddingToKnowledgeSource.

P15 (Onboarding flow) — already implemented; verified AiOnboardingModal.tsx (4-step Radix
  Dialog wizard, persona selection, localStorage guard), showOnboarding state in
  AiAssistantPage.tsx, aiHub.onboarding.* i18n keys.

P16 (PlanExecution in AiAgentRuntimeService) — add UsePlanningMode bool to AiAgent entity
  with EnablePlanningMode()/DisablePlanningMode() methods; EF config + migration;
  TryBuildExecutionPlanAsync private method (non-fatal planning step before main inference);
  plan prepended to system prompt; PlanSummary field added to AgentExecutionResult.

P17 (VS Code extension scaffold) — tools/ide-extensions/vscode/ with package.json,
  tsconfig.json, src/extension.ts (chat + configure commands, HTTP client), README.md.

P18 (Agent Marketplace ratings) — GetAverageRatingAsync on IAiFeedbackRepository;
  infrastructure implementation via execution join; MarketplaceAgentDto.AverageRating;
  Handler backward-compatible (single-arg overload for existing tests);
  batch-load ratings in Handler.

Tests added: EmbeddingIndexJobTests (3), PlanExecutionIntegrationTests (3),
  GetAgentMarketplaceWithRatingsTests (2). Zero compiler errors. TS: clean.

